SUMMARY:Van Vleck Online Specialty Plant Sale
DESCRIPTION:Each winter we feature fabulous special trees and shrubs at our Online Plant Sale that are NOT available for purchase at our popular Spring Plant Sale in early May. These items are larger and often harder-to-find plants. Items can be ordered through the link above starting February 12th until March 1st and then picked up at Van Vleck during the in-person Spring Sale May 1- 3.\nThe sale link will open on February 12th at 9AM on our website: https://montclairfoundation.org/event/van-vleck-online-plant-sale-2026/2026-02-12/ \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/van-vleck-online-specialty-plant-sale/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, NJ\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community
