SUMMARY:Montclair Music Club Concert March 2nd
DESCRIPTION:MONTCLAIR MUSIC CLUB will host their next program at Presbyterian Church of Upper Montclair\, 53 Norwood Ave.\, Monday morning\, March 2nd\, at 11:30 am. This will be the only daytime program of the season. \nPerforming on this program will the Long Duo\, a piano duo\, and the Madison String Quartet. The Long Duo will be performing pieces by Schubert\, Mendelssohn\, Schoenfield\, their own “Fantasy on the Ali Mountain”\, and their arrangement of “America” from West Side Story. The Madison String Quartet will perform the Shostakovich String Quartet No. 8 and El Diablo Suelto by Fernandez. Please join us for this outstanding  concert opportunity\, free and open to the public. Reception immediately following the program. Enter the church on the east side of the building at the double doors. We look forward to seeing you there! MMC is a 501(c)(3) organization. Donations requested at the registration desk and/or the website: https://montclairmusicclub.org/donate/ Follow on the MMC FB page: MontclairMusic Club – Home | Facebook Find highlights of the 2025-26 season at https://YouTube.com/@MontclairMusicClub \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/montclair-music-club-concert-march-2nd/
LOCATION:The Presbyterian Church of Upper Montclair\, 53 Norwood Avenue\, Upper Montclair\, NJ\, 07043\, United States
CATEGORIES:Live Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Montclair-Music-Club-Program-March-2-2026-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Music Club":MAILTO:lpaparatto@gmail.com
GEO:40.8442101;-74.2021313
