SUMMARY:Cherish the Ladies
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for an unforgettable evening of Irish music and celebration with the Grammy-nominated supergroup Cherish The Ladies. They ignite stages worldwide with their signature blend of virtuosic instrumental skill\, beautiful vocals\, and dazzling step dancing. \nIrish Traditions with Heart – For four decades\, the group’s dynamic performances have brought classic Irish melodies\, good cheer\, and authentic spirit to audiences around the globe. “[Cherish the Ladies] expands the annals of Irish music in America…the music is passionate\, tender\, and rambunctious.” (The New York Times) \nAcclaimed Musicianship and Showmanship – Their shows deliver an astonishing array of virtuosity\, humor\, and heartfelt connection through time-honored tunes\, modern arrangements\, and foot-stomping step dancing. “It is simply impossible to imagine an audience that wouldn’t enjoy what they do.” (The Boston Globe) \nA Living Legacy – Whether celebrating the holidays\, collaborating with symphony orchestras\, or starring in Emmy-winning specials\, they blaze forward\, passing on the music of their ancestors and inspiring new generations to join the dance. \nExperience the perfect blend of artistry\, tradition\, and contagious joy with Cherish The Ladies\, a powerful testament to both Irish heritage and trailblazing musicianship. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/cherish-the-ladies-2/
LOCATION:South Orange Performing Arts Center (SOPAC)\, One SOPAC Way\, South Orange Village\, 07079\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art & Culture,Live Music
