SUMMARY:First Fridays
DESCRIPTION:First Friday is taking over Lackawanna Station and we’re in on the fun. All the shops and spots will be open\, activated\, and buzzing – so come wander\, connect\, and make a night of it. \nAnd while you’re here\, RecRoom is the spot to post up and actually get something done – work\, study\, read\, craft\, knock out admin\, or just catch up with a friend. \nMembers: no need to use a check in – your time tonight is FREE! Please RSVP below to help with our head count. \nEveryone else: $10 gets you access to the space\, free coffee + tea + hot chocolate\, fast WiFi\, stocked bathroom\, & more. \nPop in and be part of the energy! Adults only please. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
