SUMMARY:SHOOP! Special House Edition w/ Aaron Dae (Razor-N-Tape NYC) & Cher La Luna
DESCRIPTION:A return to 90s house—deep grooves\, timeless energy\, and a dancefloor built for movement.\nSHOOP returns on March 6th with a special all–90s house music edition\, created as a tribute to the sound and spirit of the era that shaped modern dancefloors. \nThis night is about deep grooves\, soulful rhythms\, and the timeless energy of 90s house music. Expect carefully selected records\, long blends\, and a room built for movement—music rooted in history and played with intention. \nJoining the night is Aaron Dae\, making this edition of SHOOP feel like a full-circle moment. With shared roots in the underground house scene and decades of experience between them\, the night brings together memory\, atmosphere\, and a deep respect for the dancefloor. \nThis is a space for dancers\, listeners\, and those who know the feeling. \nSpecial Guest:\nAaron Dae (Razor-N-Tape Brooklyn)\nAaron Dae has been a driving force in underground dance music since the 1990s. A DJ\, promoter\, and label owner\, he is the co-head of Razor-N-Tape\, the influential NYC label and Greenpoint BK record store known for its deep connection to disco and house culture. \nAaron’s sound blends deep house\, disco\, funk\, and soul—grounded in classic dancefloor traditions and refined through decades behind the decks. \nResident DJ\nCher La Luna aka Miss Merenda\nDJ Cher La Luna is a selector shaped by the house music scenes of Philadelphia and NYC\, with roots in the 90s club and rave era. Her sets are groove-driven and soulful\, built around feeling\, flow\, and dancefloor connection. Through her SHOOP party series\, she creates nights centered on music with history\, warmth\, and intention. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/shoop-special-house-edition-w-aaron-dae-razor-n-tape-nyc-cher-la-luna/
LOCATION:Porta Montclair\, 499 Bloomfield Ave\, Montclair\, NJ\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art & Culture
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/SHOOP-w-AARON-DAE-EVENTBRITECOVER.png
ORGANIZER;CN="DJ Cher La Luna":MAILTO:djcherlaluna@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
